Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:56.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,（法語）我有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:00.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你有…         - 你有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:02.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他有…         - 他有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我們有…         - 我們有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他們有…         - 他們有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你們有…         - 你們有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:14.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他們有…        - 他們有…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,《環形使者》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:44.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Time travel has not yet been invented.\N{\rCHT}雖然時間旅行現在尚未被發明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:47.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,But 30 years from now, it will have been.\N{\rCHT}但三十年後就會出現{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,It will be instantly outlawed...\N{\rCHT}它一出現  即被認定為非法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:57.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,...used only in secret by the largest criminal organizations.\N{\rCHT}只被大型犯罪組織秘密使用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:02.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,美國堪薩斯州    2044年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's nearly impossible to dispose of a body in the future.\N{\rCHT}由於將來基因標誌技術的發展{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm told. Tagging techniques, whatnot.\N{\rCHT}想處理掉一具屍首幾乎是不可能的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:19.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,So when these criminal organizations in the future need someone gone...\N{\rCHT}所以  當未來的犯罪組織想把誰做掉時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:25.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,...they use specialized assassins in our present called loopers.\N{\rCHT}他們要雇傭一些活在當下的特殊殺手"環形使者"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:30.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,And so my employers in the future nab the target\N{\rCHT}於是  我在未來的老闆只需抓住目標{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,They zap him back to me, their looper.\N{\rCHT}把他傳送回來給我  他們的"環形殺手"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,He appears, hands tied and head sacked.\N{\rCHT}目標會被反綁雙手  頭被套住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I do the necessaries.\N{\rCHT}我幹完收尾工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:42.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Collect my silver.\N{\rCHT}拿走屬於我的傭銀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the target is vanished from the future...\N{\rCHT}這個人就在未來永遠消失了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and I've just disposed of a body that technically does not exist.\N{\rCHT}而我只是處理掉了一個嚴格意義上來說並不存在的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Clean.\N{\rCHT}乾淨俐落{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:05.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,(法語)- 早上好啊  喬         - 早上好  碧垂斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How's the French?           - Slow.\N{\rCHT}- 法語學得怎麼樣了？ - 進步很慢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How's the coffee?        - Burnt.\N{\rCHT}- 咖啡怎麼樣？ - 剛煮好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,（當鋪）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:35.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,（請將槍置於此箱）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two, Jed.\N{\rCHT}兩個  傑德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Joe.\N{\rCHT}嗨  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Be at the club tonight?        - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 晚上去夜店嗎？   - 去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Four, Jed.\N{\rCHT}四個  傑德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,（法語）很高興…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好  小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, walk around.\N{\rCHT}你繞過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:04.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Around the bike. I'm not kidding! Wide, around, you shit!\N{\rCHT}繞過我的車  我不是開玩笑的  滾遠點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Rude! If you had a mama, she didn't raise you right.\N{\rCHT}有娘生沒娘養的傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's funny. I'm going to pick your mother up later on my bike...\N{\rCHT}笑死人了  我一會兒就用摩托載上你媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- and I'm gonna take my blunderbuss...        - Hey, Seth.\N{\rCHT}- 再用我的雷筒短槍…    - 嗨  塞思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Joe.        - That's new.\N{\rCHT}- 嗨  喬     - 買新車啦？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.\N{\rCHT}嗯  謝了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goddamn thing won't fucking start.\N{\rCHT}操  又他媽發動不起來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you going to the Belle?\N{\rCHT}去"百麗"夜店？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So you bought a slat bike?        - Yup.\N{\rCHT}- 你買了輛滑板摩托？ - 沒錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,How much that thing set you back? How much?\N{\rCHT}那玩意值不少錢吧？值多少？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was gonna pull up in it tonight.\N{\rCHT}本來打算今晚騎著拉風一下的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, congratulations. You're pulling up with me instead.\N{\rCHT}你現在坐我車裡也挺拉風的啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't. If we're going in, don't do that.\N{\rCHT}別  等我們到地方  你就別耍這個了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Chicks dig TKs.        - They do not.\N{\rCHT}- 妞都迷會念力驅動的人啊   - 你想多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:46.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, they do.          - It's tacky. Don't do it.\N{\rCHT}- 她們就是喜歡   - 太沒風度了  別玩這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:52.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,About 10 percent of the population has this TK mutation.\N{\rCHT}十分之一的人生來就能以念力驅物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,When it first appeared,\N{\rCHT}這種特異功能第一次被發現時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,everyone thought we were gonna get superheroes.\N{\rCHT}大家都以為找到了超能英雄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:06:00.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,But it turns out this was it. Now it's a bunch of assholes...\N{\rCHT}但現在看來  他們只是一幫蠢貨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,...think they're blowing your mind floating quarters.\N{\rCHT}自以為能讓硬幣飄起來就能泡遍天下的妹子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's like this whole town.\N{\rCHT}整座城市的人都這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Big heads, small potatoes.\N{\rCHT}人人自命不凡  命命皆如草芥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Full house tonight, Joe.        - We'll stick backstage.\N{\rCHT}- 今天場滿了  喬    - 我們就去後臺看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Just meeting up.        - Packing your blunderbusses?\N{\rCHT}- 見個人就走     - 又帶了槍？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hardly. Right, Seth?        - I'm with Joe.\N{\rCHT}- 沒有  對吧  塞思    - 我和喬一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Just meeting up, in and out.        - Go on.\N{\rCHT}- 見個人馬上就走    - 去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Suzie!\N{\rCHT}蘇西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey!        - You working a shift tonight?\N{\rCHT}- 嘿     - 你今天輪班？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.        - Yeah?\N{\rCHT}- 嗯    - 嗯？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,A gat man bought me out already for the night.\N{\rCHT}但今晚已經有人要帶我出場了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sweetie, I've got to work.\N{\rCHT}親愛的  我要工作了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Joe.\N{\rCHT}喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What?        - Zach. He's in there right now with Abe.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼了？    - 紮克  他和亞伯在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- For what?        - Closed his loop.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼了？    - 他封環了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,No shit?\N{\rCHT}不是吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:27.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a reason we're called loopers.\N{\rCHT}我們之所以叫"環形使者"是因為{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:32.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,When we sign up for this job, taking out the future's garbage...\N{\rCHT}當我們決定做這行  幫未來掃清障礙時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:36.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,...we also agree to a very specific proviso.\N{\rCHT}我們同時也簽下了一條非常特別的協議{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Time travel in the future is so illegal...\N{\rCHT}在未來  時間旅行是非法的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,...that when our employers want to close our contracts...\N{\rCHT}所以當老闆想終止與我們的合同時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:49.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,...they'll also want to erase any trace of their relationship with us ever existing.\N{\rCHT}他們也想一次性抹掉與我們有關的任何痕跡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,So if we're still alive 30 years from now...\N{\rCHT}因此如果三十年後我們還有幸不死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:59.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,...they'll find our older self, zap him back to us...\N{\rCHT}他們會找到將來的我們  並送還回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and we'll kill him like any otherjob.\N{\rCHT}然後我們就會像幹掉其他人一樣幹掉自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is called closing your loop.\N{\rCHT}這就是所謂的"封環"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,You get a golden payday, you get a handshake...\N{\rCHT}傭銀會變成傭金  大家會跟你握手道別{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and you get released from your contract.\N{\rCHT}你從此自由了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the next 30 years.\N{\rCHT}好好享受接下來的三十年吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:22.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,This job doesn't tend to attract the most forward-thinking people.\N{\rCHT}所以那些想活命的人都對這工作敬而遠之{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:25.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we celebrating?\N{\rCHT}那咱們開始慶祝吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look out!\N{\rCHT}小心！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,（法語）早啊  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:42.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,（法語）很高興見到你  碧垂斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,（法語）哎呀  進步神速啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,What, fourth loop closed this month?\N{\rCHT}這個月都有四個封環的了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Loop closed. Here we go.\N{\rCHT}封環成功！幹！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:12.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Loop closed, baby!\N{\rCHT}封環成功  寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Seth?\N{\rCHT}塞思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,They could be here any minute.\N{\rCHT}他們隨時都會來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Are they here?        - No. Who?\N{\rCHT}- 他們不在吧？ - 沒  你說誰？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:13.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, Christ. Joe, Christ!\N{\rCHT}天哪  喬  天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing?        - Give me the gun.\N{\rCHT}- 你要幹嘛？ - 把槍給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. That's smart.\N{\rCHT}好  明智的做法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Get away from the window.        - Christ, Joe.\N{\rCHT}- 離窗子遠點    - 天哪  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Just quiet down.        - You can protect me.\N{\rCHT}- 安靜點    - 你會保護我吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So they...        - What did you do?\N{\rCHT}- 這樣他們…   - 你怎麼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:27.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez. This is like a nightmare.\N{\rCHT}天哪  真是場噩夢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare.\N{\rCHT}這真是場噩夢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,I knew then what he did, so I don't know why I asked.\N{\rCHT}我突然明白他怎麼了  我不懂自己為什麼還要問他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,What did you do?\N{\rCHT}你怎麼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:40.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,He... He was singing.\N{\rCHT}他…他在唱歌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:46.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Through the gag and sack, but I could hear the tune.\N{\rCHT}雖然罩了麻袋  我還是能聽出調子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Deep memories...\N{\rCHT}我還記得…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:55.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,...my mom in a dark room taking care of me, singing that tune.\N{\rCHT}那是以前我媽晚上哄我的時候給我唱的歌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:12:01.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Once I knew he was me....\N{\rCHT}我知道他就是我…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Joe, I couldn't.\N{\rCHT}喬  我下不了手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:12.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I couldn't. I had to see.\N{\rCHT}我做不到  我必須得看看我自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:18.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,He told me... I remember, he told me...\N{\rCHT}我記得  他和我說…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,...there's a new holy terror boss man in the future...\N{\rCHT}在未來來了一個可怕的新老大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and he's closing all the loops.\N{\rCHT}他要封掉我們所有人的環{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Rainmaker, they call him.\N{\rCHT}大家叫他"喚雨師"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:34.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,He told me it. Then he wanted a cigarette.\N{\rCHT}他說完後  又說他想抽根煙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:38.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I untied him, and he gives me this look.\N{\rCHT}我給他松了綁  他就那樣看了我一眼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,And he just starts running.\N{\rCHT}然後他就跑了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I had my blunderbuss...\N{\rCHT}我握著雷筒短槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,...so I know I've got about 15 strides until he's out of my range.\N{\rCHT}知道他一旦跑出15步遠  我就殺不了他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they come and they go...\N{\rCHT}我不知道該怎麼辦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and I just watch him until he's gone.\N{\rCHT}就這麼看著他逃了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is called letting your loop run.\N{\rCHT}這就是所謂的"失環"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not a good thing.\N{\rCHT}絕對不是件好事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do I do?\N{\rCHT}我該怎麼辦？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're the only friend I've got, Joe. You've got to help me.\N{\rCHT}你是我唯一的朋友  你要幫我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a fucking idiot coming here.\N{\rCHT}你來我這兒就太他媽傻了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't be here. I'll give you some money. That's it.\N{\rCHT}你不能呆在這兒  我給你些錢  你趕緊走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:19.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Joe! A little money? Where am I gonna go?\N{\rCHT}給我些錢？我能去哪兒？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,You hop a freight train. You beat it the hell out of town.\N{\rCHT}你找輛貨車  趕緊出城{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just don't move.\N{\rCHT}別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell Court, watch the window outside.\N{\rCHT}叫考爾從外面盯著窗子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got it, window.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:40.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Kid Blue, Joe! Come on!        - Just a minute!\N{\rCHT}- 我是藍小子  喬  開門    - 等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Open this goddamn door!        - I can't do anything for you, Seth.\N{\rCHT}- 他媽的快開門！    - 我幫不了你  塞思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:47.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've got to hide me! Please, Joe! Hide me!\N{\rCHT}把我藏起來  求你了  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:51.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please! Just buy me some time and then I'll go! Please?\N{\rCHT}給我點時間  我馬上就走  求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,You gonna make me blow this door down?\N{\rCHT}你想讓我把門砸了麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hold on!\N{\rCHT}馬上來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please?\N{\rCHT}求求你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move. Move.\N{\rCHT}過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, Joe! Open up!\N{\rCHT}快點  喬  開門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}天啊…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That took a while.        - You think it's easy looking this good?\N{\rCHT}- 你小子夠久的啊   - 起來不用時間嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:32.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tye's gonna watch your apartment while we go have a talk with Abe.\N{\rCHT}泰伊會幫你看房子  你跟我去見亞伯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's coffee in the tin.\N{\rCHT}罐子裡有咖啡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give me two minutes.\N{\rCHT}給我兩分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Know why they call that pea shooter of yours a blunderbuss?\N{\rCHT}你知道為什麼這玩意兒叫雷筒短槍嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because it's impossible to hit anything farther than 15 yards.\N{\rCHT}因為它射不中15碼以外的靶子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Impossible to miss anything closer.\N{\rCHT}但也不可能射偏15碼以內的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a gun for fuck-up turkeys.\N{\rCHT}這是標準的蠢貨配槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not like a gat.\N{\rCHT}不像我這把手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,A gat has range.\N{\rCHT}手槍有射程{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Accuracy.\N{\rCHT}也有精准度{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kid, cut it out. Don't blow your other foot off.\N{\rCHT}別玩了  不然你另一條腿也要廢了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Fuck!        - What the hell is going on out there?\N{\rCHT}- 操    - 他媽的外面鬧什麼呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How you doing, Abe?        - Hey, Joe.\N{\rCHT}- 最近還好嗎  亞伯？ - 嘿  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,You didn't shoot your other foot off, did you, Kid?\N{\rCHT}小子  你沒把另一條腿也打殘吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}沒事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:23.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,My great-grandfather told my grandfather, "Men are like spiders."\N{\rCHT}我曾祖父對我祖父說過   "男人是蜘蛛"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,"It's the little ones you've got to be careful of."\N{\rCHT}"越是小個子  你越要小心"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't know I agree with that.\N{\rCHT}這句我沒聽明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah?\N{\rCHT}是麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the fuck did my great-grandfather know?\N{\rCHT}我曾祖父又他媽知道什麼呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:36.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,This man is from the future.\N{\rCHT}這個男人來自未來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:41.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,He was sent back here by the mob, a one-way ticket, to run the loopers.\N{\rCHT}他被頭頭派來這兒管理環形使者  他自己是永遠回不去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's low effort, even for Abe, so to pass the time...\N{\rCHT}對亞伯來說  這工作不費吹灰之力  為了打發時間...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,...he recruited some real muscle, the gat men. Now he runs the city.\N{\rCHT}他招了些壯漢  叫做"槍手"  他是炙手可熱的人物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Any other city, that would be impressive.\N{\rCHT}不僅這兒  所有的城市都歸他管{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,How can you kids stand to wear those chokers?\N{\rCHT}你們這些小鬼怎麼能受得了這個繞脖子的東西？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Cravats?        - Ties.\N{\rCHT}- 這個領巾    - 是領帶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous. You're aware we don't have a dress code?\N{\rCHT}沒必要啊  我們又不要求穿正裝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Fashion.        - You know... Well, you don't know.\N{\rCHT}- 潮嘛    - 你知道…好吧  你不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:19.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,The movies that you're dressing like are just copying other movies.\N{\rCHT}你按電影裡的穿  這些電影也都是互相抄的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:23.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,These goddamn 20th century affectations.\N{\rCHT}都是些20世紀的矯情玩意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do something new.\N{\rCHT}來點有創意的吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:30.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put a glowing thing around your neck or use rubberized....\N{\rCHT}戴點更炫的東西  比如橡膠做的什麼…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Just be new.        - Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 有新意就行     - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:43.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It was nice chatting with you, Abe.        - I do like you, Joe.\N{\rCHT}- 和你聊天很愉快  亞伯     - 我欣賞你  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,But we're sure enough that Seth paid you a visit.\N{\rCHT}但我知道塞思去找過你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We have to do something.        - Seth?\N{\rCHT}- 而我們必須得把這事給解決了    - 塞思？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:53.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're expecting we're gonna break your fingers with a hammer or something awful.\N{\rCHT}你肯定以為我們會用錘子敲你的手指來逼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:57.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I'm gonna defuse that tension right now. That's not gonna happen.\N{\rCHT}但是你不用緊張  我不會那樣做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:01.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is gonna happen is that I'm gonna talk for a little.\N{\rCHT}我只是要和你稍微聊一聊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not even that long.\N{\rCHT}不會很長的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna give up your friend.\N{\rCHT}然後你就會交出你的朋友了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:10.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,My friend? Seth? Sorry, I'm confused.\N{\rCHT}我朋友？塞思？對不起  我搞糊塗了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, then I'll talk a little.\N{\rCHT}好吧  那我們就來說一說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, you were the youngest looper I ever hired.\N{\rCHT}你是我雇的最年輕的環形使者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:18.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,You looked goddamn ridiculous, they said.\N{\rCHT}他們都說你不怎麼正常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Blunderbuss up to here on you.\N{\rCHT}現在你有雷筒短槍了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:24.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,They brought you in. I forget what for.\N{\rCHT}我忘了他們是因為什麼事把你逮進來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Watch shop.\N{\rCHT}我搶了手錶店{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:29.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You rolled one of our fronts, a watch shop.\N{\rCHT}對  你偷了我們的一家店{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:34.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they had you, you know. This kid, like an animal.\N{\rCHT}他們抓了你  你這個小鬼看起來特別野{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you looked at me, your hair stuck to half your face...\N{\rCHT}你盯著我  頭髮擋住了半邊臉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,...just one eye looking at me. I could see...\N{\rCHT}我只能看到你用一隻眼睛盯著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:47.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,...like seeing it happen on the TV, the bad version of your life.\N{\rCHT}就跟看電視一樣  我能看到你最糟的樣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:52.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like a vision, I could see how you'd turn bad.\N{\rCHT}我都可以看到你是如何一步步變壞的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I changed it.\N{\rCHT}所以我改變了這一切{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:59.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I cleaned you up and put a gun in your hand.\N{\rCHT}我幫你打理乾淨  給了你把槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I gave you something that was yours.        - I'm grateful for that, Abe.\N{\rCHT}- 我給你的  都是你本該有的    - 我很感激你  亞伯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:08.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I gave you something that was yours.\N{\rCHT}我給你的  都是你本該有的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I remember that kid.\N{\rCHT}我記得那小鬼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I think if you ask yourself, you ask,\N{\fn華文楷體}因此我想  如果你問自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Who would I sacrifice for what's mine?"\N{\rCHT}"為了那些本就是我的東西  我願意犧牲誰？"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think Seth would be deep and cozy inside that circle.\N{\rCHT}塞思肯定是一個好選擇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how much I know you.\N{\rCHT}我要讓你看看我有多瞭解你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:31.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not even gonna break you. I'm just gonna set you back a ways.\N{\rCHT}我不會毀了你  只是會將你打回原形{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,We know that you've been stashing half your bars.\N{\rCHT}我知道你把一半的酬金都藏起來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Which is smart, no law against it. You're gonna get out.\N{\rCHT}很聰明  沒誰規定說不行  你總有天會金盆洗手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna go overseas. Is it right? Studying up your Mandarin?\N{\rCHT}到海外去  對不對？還在學中文？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- French.        - French?\N{\rCHT}- 法語    - 法語？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:51.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,You give him up or you give us half your stash.\N{\rCHT}交出塞思  或者交出你這一半酬金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:57.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,You willing to dump your silver in the dirt for Seth?\N{\rCHT}為了塞思  你甘心丟掉這一切嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna kill him.\N{\rCHT}你會殺了他麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:13.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not if we can help it. Be too cataclysmic a change for the future.\N{\rCHT}如果別無他法  這對未來會造成毀滅性的改變{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,What we'll do is dangerous in that regards...\N{\rCHT}我們要做的事是很危險的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,...though not as dangerous as killing him.\N{\rCHT}不過不殺他更危險{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:22.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,On top of which, a man from the future runs free long enough...\N{\rCHT}最重要的是  如果放任那個未來的人潛逃太久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:26.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,...this time travel shit fries your brain like an egg.\N{\rCHT}穿越時空把你的腦袋壓得像煎蛋似的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why the fuck French?\N{\rCHT}為什麼學法語？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going to France.\N{\rCHT}我要去法國{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You should go to China.        - I'm going to France.\N{\rCHT}- 你應該去中國    - 我要去法國{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm from the future. You should go to China.\N{\rCHT}我是從未來回來的  你應該去中國{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm going to France.        - You're going....\N{\rCHT}- 我要去法國    - 你該去…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,The floor safe, under the rug.\N{\rCHT}在地毯下的保險箱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Six seven four two.\N{\rCHT}密碼是 6742{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the little ones that get you.\N{\rCHT}小個子的才會扳倒你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:14.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you kill an hour, Joe. On the house.\N{\rCHT}喬  你先在這裡逛會吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Call the doc.\N{\rCHT}叫醫生準備好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:55.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,15分鐘內{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:58.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,趕到外爾街75號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N{\rCHT}等等！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:02.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait!\N{\rCHT}等等！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:05.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N{\rCHT}等等…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:14.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, I can't remember my mother's face.\N{\rCHT}我記不清我媽媽的臉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:19.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,She used to run her hands through my hair.\N{\rCHT}只記得她用手撫摸我的頭髮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:26.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just like this.\N{\rCHT}就像這樣…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:46.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I just let my best friend get killed tonight.\N{\rCHT}我今晚剛害死了我最好的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:49.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,For silver.\N{\rCHT}為了錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:24:56.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}見鬼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.03,0:24:58.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}耶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.29,0:25:00.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}真是見鬼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.46,0:25:06.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\N{\rCHT}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.50,0:25:10.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give you some money.\N{\rCHT}我給你些錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.59,0:25:14.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been stashing my silver for years and I'm gonna give you half of it.\N{\rCHT}這些年我存了些錢  我給你一半{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.34,0:25:17.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can raise your kid right.\N{\rCHT}你就可以不做這行了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.64,0:25:19.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna give me half your silver?\N{\rCHT}你要分我一半的銀子？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:23.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Silver's got strings. I got my job.\N{\rCHT}銀子是有用  但我有我的工作…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.48,0:25:27.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got yours.\N{\rCHT}你也有你的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.23,0:25:31.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's sweet of you to worry about me, but I'm doing fine.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你為我著想  不過我幹得挺好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.65,0:25:36.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just stick to services rendered.\N{\rCHT}這種單純的服務關係不是很好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.49,0:25:43.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is this what you want?\N{\rCHT}這不就是你想要的嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:28:02.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,"跳上火車出城去  快跑"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:41.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's 24 there. I'm keeping count.\N{\rCHT}有24塊  我數過了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.78,0:29:45.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two more trips should just do it.\N{\rCHT}再來兩趟就行了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.47,0:30:09.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goddamn it!\N{\rCHT}操！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.64,0:30:15.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kid, I'm sorry! Tell Abe I'm gonna fix this!\N{\rCHT}對不住了  跟亞伯說我能搞定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.56,0:30:19.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tell him I'm gonna find my loop and I'm gonna kill him! Tell Abe...\N{\rCHT}我一定能找到他   我一定會殺了他…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.30,0:32:09.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,上海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.43,0:36:32.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit!\N{\rCHT}操！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.46,0:36:58.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got any aspirin?\N{\rCHT}有阿司匹林麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.59,0:37:00.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,All of them, please.\N{\rCHT}全要了  謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.38,0:37:06.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll take that coat, too.\N{\rCHT}這外套也要了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.11,0:37:28.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在做什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.54,0:37:34.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Joe, I told you to run.\N{\rCHT}喬  你在做什麼？我不是叫你快跑嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:37:59.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, you idiot.\N{\rCHT}別犯傻  你個白癡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.33,0:38:13.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fucking Kid Blue.\N{\rCHT}該死的藍小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.04,0:38:16.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,About two more trips should do it.\N{\rCHT}還有兩趟就行了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.29,0:38:55.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.23,0:39:19.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You stupid little shit.\N{\rCHT}你個傻逼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.49,0:39:31.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pound the pavement, sweep the train yard.\N{\rCHT}從人行道過去  搜查火車場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.78,0:39:35.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Every second that passes is bad. Get on it.\N{\rCHT}一秒也不能耽誤！快！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.75,0:39:38.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stupid little shit.\N{\rCHT}廢物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.37,0:39:40.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can fix this.\N{\rCHT}我可以補救{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.71,0:39:43.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I can find him!        - Go home.\N{\rCHT}- 我會找到他的   - 回去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.92,0:39:45.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let the grownups work.\N{\rCHT}還是讓大人們來吧…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.01,0:39:48.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kid Blue.\N{\rCHT}藍小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.42,0:40:30.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,You bastard. How do I find you?\N{\rCHT}你個混蛋  怎樣才能把你找出來？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.74,0:40:59.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,列印中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.39,0:42:08.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,去找碧垂斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.55,0:42:39.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Coffee?\N{\rCHT}咖啡？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.85,0:42:43.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.02,0:42:46.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Black. And some water.\N{\rCHT}黑咖啡  再來些水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.60,0:42:48.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anything else?\N{\rCHT}還要什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.02,0:42:50.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,We eating?\N{\rCHT}在這裡吃東西嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.36,0:42:55.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I ordered something.        - Steak and eggs. Rare and scrambled.\N{\rCHT}- 我已經點過了    - 牛排配雞蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.19,0:42:57.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two steak and eggs, coming up.\N{\rCHT}兩份牛排配雞蛋  兩位稍等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.49,0:43:04.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Must hurt.\N{\rCHT}一定很疼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.66,0:43:08.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I wasn't sure you'd remember her.        - I put it together.\N{\rCHT}- 我不確定你是否記得她    - 慢慢就想起來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.12,0:43:10.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Clever.\N{\rCHT}聰明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.59,0:43:21.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, there's another girl who works here on the weekends.\N{\rCHT}這兒還有個週末上班的姑娘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.97,0:43:26.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jen?        - Right. Less letters.\N{\rCHT}- 珍妮？   - 對  筆劃少些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.35,0:43:29.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,That'd be better.\N{\rCHT}更省事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.15,0:43:38.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,How's your French coming?\N{\rCHT}法語學得怎麼樣了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:42.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good. You gonna tell me I ought to be learning Mandarin?\N{\rCHT}還行  你要跟我說你怎麼學的普通話嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.82,0:43:44.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I never regretted learning French.\N{\rCHT}我從未後悔學了法語{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.91,0:43:48.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know you have a gun between your legs.\N{\rCHT}我知道你雙腿間藏了把槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.66,0:43:52.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,No? Well, you'll get it eventually.\N{\rCHT}不懂？好吧  你以後會懂的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.29,0:43:55.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Obviously.        - All right, listen.\N{\rCHT}- 當然    - 好了  聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.38,0:43:59.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a hard situation, but we both know how this has to go down.\N{\rCHT}現在是一個困局  但我們都事態將會如何發展{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.22,0:44:01.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't let you walk away from this diner.\N{\rCHT}這次我不能再放你活著出去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.72,0:44:04.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is my life now. I earned it. You had yours already.\N{\rCHT}這是我的生活  我掙來的  你已經享受過你的了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.80,0:44:09.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,So why don't you do what old men do and die? Get the fuck out of my way.\N{\rCHT}你為什麼不願意像其他人一樣去死呢？別擋我的路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.73,0:44:13.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take your gun out from between your legs and do it?\N{\rCHT}那就把你腿間的槍拔出來動手吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.07,0:44:17.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Boy.\N{\rCHT}小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.99,0:44:25.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's hard staring into your eyes.\N{\rCHT}很難直視你的眼睛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.54,0:44:30.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's too strange.        - Your face looks backwards.\N{\rCHT}- 感覺太詭異了    - 你的臉讓我看到了過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.92,0:44:36.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you know what's gonna happen? You've done all this already?\N{\rCHT}那你知道將來會發生什麼嗎？你不是都經歷過了嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.34,0:44:38.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about time travel shit.\N{\rCHT}我不想提時間旅行這些爛事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.05,0:44:42.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we start talking about it, we're gonna be here all day.\N{\rCHT}一旦說起來  三天三夜都講不完{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.26,0:44:43.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Making diagrams with straws.\N{\rCHT}還得一邊說一邊給你畫圖示意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.09,0:44:47.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It doesn't matter.        - I hurt myself, it changes your body.\N{\rCHT}- 這不重要    - 如果我受傷  你的身體也會出問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.26,0:44:50.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Does what I do change your memories?        - It doesn't matter!\N{\rCHT}- 我現在做的事會改變你的記憶嗎？  - 這不重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.90,0:45:04.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,My memory is cloudy.\N{\rCHT}我的記憶很模糊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.99,0:45:07.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a cloud.\N{\rCHT}像一團迷霧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.49,0:45:10.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because my memories aren't really memories.\N{\rCHT}因為我的記憶並不是真實的記憶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.08,0:45:13.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're just one possible eventuality now.\N{\rCHT}現在它們只是變成了一種可能性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.71,0:45:21.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they grow clearer or cloudier as they become more or less likely.\N{\rCHT}它們或者漸漸清晰  或者因可能性變小而更加模糊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.30,0:45:25.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,But then they get to the present moment, and they're instantly clear again.\N{\rCHT}但當它們變成當下時  就會突然又變清晰了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.47,0:45:29.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can remember what you do after you do it.\N{\rCHT}我會很清楚你做過的每件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.64,0:45:33.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,And it hurts.\N{\rCHT}很疼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.19,0:45:36.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,So even when we're apart...\N{\rCHT}所以現在即使我們分開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.48,0:45:38.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- you can remember what I do after?        - Yes.\N{\rCHT}- 我做了什麼你也一清二楚嗎？   - 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.86,0:45:43.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,But this is a precise description of a fuzzy mechanism.\N{\rCHT}但這只是對一個模糊機制的理智描述{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.24,0:45:45.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's messy.\N{\rCHT}真的一片混亂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.11,0:45:47.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,All I know... I know two things.\N{\rCHT}我所知道的  只有兩件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.12,0:45:52.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know what's happening in my head. And I know that you're gonna meet her.\N{\rCHT}我只知道我知道的  我知道你還會遇見她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.29,0:45:59.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who?\N{\rCHT}誰？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.97,0:46:07.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's gonna save your life.\N{\rCHT}她會拯救你的生命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.97,0:46:15.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,For a long time, she thought we'd....\N{\rCHT}她一直都希望…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.64,0:46:18.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'd have a baby.\N{\rCHT}我們能有個孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.77,0:46:24.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,She'd have been a great mother.\N{\rCHT}她會成為一個好母親的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.20,0:46:29.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,- She wanted it so much.        - Yeah, but she...?\N{\rCHT}- 她是多麼的希望   - 但是她…？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.16,0:46:31.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,How...?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.16,0:46:35.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,So she saves my life?\N{\rCHT}你說她救了我？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.16,0:46:36.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.50,0:46:39.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at your life.\N{\rCHT}看看你活成了什麼樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.75,0:46:42.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a killer. And a junkie.\N{\rCHT}你是個殺手  一個癮君子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.59,0:46:44.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,A fucking child mentality.\N{\rCHT}還他媽的心智不成熟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.88,0:46:48.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,"What's mine." "My life." Save your life. You're asking me how?\N{\rCHT}什麼叫我的命？不是救了你的？還問我怎麼救的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.72,0:46:51.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,The question is why. Why would someone sacrifice their life?\N{\rCHT}問題是為什麼有人會甘願犧牲自己？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.05,0:46:54.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cut your high and mighty bullshit. I don't need my life...\N{\rCHT}少廢話  我不需要我的生命…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.85,0:46:57.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shut your fucking child mouth.\N{\rCHT}你他媽的給我閉嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.73,0:47:01.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're so self-absorbed and stupid.\N{\rCHT}你又蠢又自以為是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.73,0:47:04.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,And she's gonna clean you up and she's gonna....\N{\rCHT}她會蕩滌你的心靈  她會…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.66,0:47:17.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna take her love like a sponge.\N{\rCHT}你就像塊海綿  吸幹了她的愛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.33,0:47:20.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you think, "Maybe I'm clear of the past.\N{\rCHT}你認為  "我已經跟過去徹底劃清界限了"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.75,0:47:22.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm safe."\N{\rCHT}"我應該安全了"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.13,0:47:25.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yesterday.\N{\rCHT}直到昨天…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.80,0:47:28.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yesterday what?\N{\rCHT}昨天怎麼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.26,0:47:31.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thirty years from now is yesterday.\N{\rCHT}我說的昨天是30年後的昨天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.39,0:47:35.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna remember it.\N{\rCHT}你要記住它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.32,0:47:48.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell you what happens...\N{\rCHT}我會告訴你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.28,0:47:52.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,...to this beautiful woman who saves your worthless fucking life.\N{\rCHT}這個拯救了你垃圾人生的美麗女人遭受了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.20,0:48:38.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of the Rainmaker?\N{\rCHT}聽說過喚雨師嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.58,0:48:43.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Seth said that night.\N{\rCHT}聽過  那天晚上塞思說過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.25,0:48:47.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,New boss in the future? He used the words "holy terror."\N{\rCHT}未來的新老大  說是"極度恐怖".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.55,0:48:50.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A reign of terror.\N{\rCHT}沒錯  恐怖統治{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.42,0:48:54.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mass executions. Vagrant purges. Everywhere at once.\N{\rCHT}大規模處決  遍地搜索  清除流浪者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.47,0:48:57.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Legend is the Rainmaker came out of nowhere.\N{\rCHT}最恐怖的是  沒人知道他的來頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.26,0:49:01.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,In the span of six months, he took total control of the five major syndicates.\N{\rCHT}僅僅半年  他就完全掌握了五個核心財團{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.52,0:49:03.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That'd take an army.        - He didn't have an army.\N{\rCHT}- 那需要軍隊才行    - 但他沒有軍隊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.06,0:49:06.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,The story is that he did it alone.\N{\rCHT}傳說他一直是孤身一人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.06,0:49:09.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Alone alone.        - So how did he do it?\N{\rCHT}- 單槍匹馬   - 那他是怎麼做到的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.36,0:49:13.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the mystery. There's no pictures of him. Even if it is a him. It's insane.\N{\rCHT}這是個謎  沒人見過他的相片  甚至連性別都不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.90,0:49:18.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,There are stories he has a synthetic jaw, saw his mom shot, shit like that.\N{\rCHT}他的人造下巴  他曾親眼目睹母親被殺之類的傳聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.58,0:49:20.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Word spread through the ex-looper grapevine...\N{\rCHT}都是那些已解約的環形使者傳出來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.12,0:49:25.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,...because the first thing he did was start closing loops. All of them.\N{\rCHT}因為他做的第一件事就是封環  封所有人的環{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.38,0:49:31.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what this is? This number?\N{\rCHT}你知道這是什麼嗎？這組數字？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.13,0:49:33.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dale, wait. Slow down.\N{\rCHT}等等  慢點說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.51,0:49:37.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,It could lead us to the Rainmaker, Joe! It's in the hospital records.\N{\rCHT}這可以幫我們找到喚雨師  喬  這是在醫院記錄裡找到的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.30,0:49:40.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Write this down: 0, 7, 1 , 5, 3...\N{\rCHT}你記下來  0, 7, 1, 5, 3,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.64,0:49:43.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,9, 0, 2, 9, 3, 5!{\r}\N{\fs18\fnCronos Pro Subhead}...9, 0, 2, 9, 3, 5!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.07,0:49:55.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a piece of identifying information on the Rainmaker.\N{\rCHT}這是可以驗證喚雨師身份的資訊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.16,0:50:01.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's here. He lives here now. In this county.\N{\rCHT}他就在這兒  就住在這個鎮子裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.66,0:50:03.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna use this to find him.\N{\rCHT}我會用這個找到他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:06.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna kill him.\N{\rCHT}然後殺了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.25,0:50:08.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stop him from killing my wife.\N{\rCHT}阻止他殺害我的妻子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.63,0:50:12.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fuck you. And your wife. None of this concerns me.\N{\rCHT}去你的！還有你老婆！這事跟我一點關係都沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.76,0:50:15.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- This is gonna happen...        - It happened to you.\N{\rCHT}- 這也是你的事…     - 這是你的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.22,0:50:19.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to happen to me. You got her picture right there in my watch?\N{\rCHT}不是我的！你把她的相片放在我的懷錶裡了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.60,0:50:22.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Show me the picture. As soon as I see her, I walk away.\N{\rCHT}給我看看她的相片  等我遇到她  我馬上走開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.60,0:50:25.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll fucking marry someone else. Promise.\N{\rCHT}我他媽的和別人結婚  我保證{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.64,0:50:29.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,When I see that picture, that fog inside your brain should just...\N{\rCHT}所以只要我看到那照片  你霧濛濛的腦子裡…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.31,0:50:32.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,...swallow up all the memories, right? She'll be gone.\N{\rCHT}關於她的記憶就會立刻消散  對嗎？她就會消失{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.61,0:50:35.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,- If you give her up, she'll be safe.        - Give her up?\N{\rCHT}- 你別管她  她就安全了    - 別管她？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.11,0:50:38.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, give her up! You're the one that got her killed.\N{\rCHT}對  不管她  就是因為你她才會死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.58,0:50:40.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,If she never meets you, she's safe.\N{\rCHT}如果她從沒遇見你  她就會很安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.24,0:50:42.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't understand. We don't have to give her up.\N{\rCHT}你不懂  我們不能不管她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.08,0:50:47.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna give her up. I'm gonna save her.\N{\rCHT}我不會不管她  我一定要救她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.10,0:51:04.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get to the fields. We can lose them in the fields.\N{\rCHT}往田裡跑  就能甩掉他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.02,0:51:08.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hop a train. Get out of town!\N{\rCHT}找輛火車！離開這兒！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.13,0:51:37.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell is everybody doing? You wait for my signal!\N{\rCHT}你們都他媽的在幹嘛？都等我的信號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.59,0:51:40.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Out back! He's running!        - He ran out the back!\N{\rCHT}- 在後面  他跑了    - 他往後跑了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.73,0:51:52.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit!\N{\rCHT}媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.11,0:52:00.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alive!\N{\rCHT}要活的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.70,0:52:08.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fuck! Shit! Come on, come on!\N{\rCHT}操！廢物！快點！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.70,0:52:11.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, you piece of shit! Come on!\N{\rCHT}快點！你個廢物！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.76,0:52:23.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Get the tracker! The tracker!        - Go! Go!\N{\rCHT}- 拿追蹤器來！追蹤器！  - 快！快！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.59,0:52:25.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fuck! Fuck!\N{\rCHT}操！操！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.93,0:52:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.62,0:54:14.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, baby. Time to get up.\N{\rCHT}寶貝  該起床了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.91,0:54:57.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen up, fucker!\N{\rCHT}聽好了  混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.41,0:55:03.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have shot and buried three vagrants in the past year!\N{\rCHT}去年我殺了三個流浪漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.46,0:55:07.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I don't care what hobo sob story you've got.\N{\rCHT}我不管你無家可歸的故事有多感人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.34,0:55:10.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I get a dozen a week, pal. It cuts no cash with me.\N{\rCHT}我每週都要聽很多  老娘不買帳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.97,0:55:16.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,But if you show your face here again, I will cut you the fuck in half!\N{\rCHT}如果你敢再在這裡出現  我他媽會把你打成兩截{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.35,0:56:01.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, you found him.\N{\rCHT}你找到他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.10,0:56:05.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tracking Seth's bike, that was clever.\N{\rCHT}追蹤塞思的摩托信號  很聰明嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.65,0:56:08.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then you rustled up a posse and went out to get him.\N{\rCHT}然後你就搞了一幫人去抓他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.94,0:56:12.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I could do it again.        - You can fuck up again? Really?\N{\rCHT}- 再給我一次機會   - 讓你再搞砸一次嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.49,0:56:14.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got too much riding, Kid.\N{\rCHT}我有點不耐煩了  小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.91,0:56:18.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't afford a fuck-up playing cowboy.\N{\rCHT}我可用不起一個隻會壞事的牛仔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.75,0:56:21.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put your gat on the table.\N{\rCHT}把手槍放桌上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.85,0:56:42.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to say I did good.\N{\rCHT}我只是希望你能誇我一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.94,0:56:47.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted.\N{\rCHT}我想要的就這麼多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.98,0:56:51.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is all I have.\N{\rCHT}我能做的也就這麼多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.91,0:57:00.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please give me one more chance?\N{\rCHT}求你再給我一次機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.91,0:57:04.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him here alive and hold him.\N{\rCHT}我會把他活著帶回來…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.96,0:57:07.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you can put a bullet in his brain yourself.\N{\rCHT}你可以親手殺了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.13,0:57:10.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,No!\N{\rCHT}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.19,0:58:10.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's there?\N{\rCHT}喂  是誰？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.99,0:58:19.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! I will shoot you.\N{\rCHT}別動  不然我開槍了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.79,0:58:24.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,You stop! Stop right there!\N{\rCHT}站住！不許動！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.17,0:58:30.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to stop! You stop!\N{\rCHT}我說站住！站住！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.43,0:58:46.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,（請幫幫啞巴  食物  上帝保佑你）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:03.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Head's splitting apart.\N{\rCHT}頭快裂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.37,0:59:05.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,- My head.        - Hey.\N{\rCHT}- 我的頭   - 嘿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.12,0:59:09.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look up at the light. Look up at me.\N{\rCHT}抬頭看看燈  看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.29,0:59:10.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,How long since you dropped?\N{\rCHT}你上次滴完是什麼時候？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.92,0:59:12.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Dropped?        - Dropped.\N{\rCHT}- 滴什麼    - 滴眼液{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.46,0:59:15.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- A day.        - A day.\N{\rCHT}- 一天前    - 一天前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.55,0:59:16.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't feel my legs.\N{\rCHT}我的腿沒知覺了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.09,0:59:19.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're going through withdrawal, you fucking junkie.\N{\rCHT}那是因為你毒癮上來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.97,0:59:22.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You gotta help me. I'm gonna die.\N{\rCHT}幫幫我  我要死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.47,0:59:25.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.\N{\rCHT}我很渴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.10,0:59:28.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Water. Water!\N{\rCHT}水  水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.04,0:59:46.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thirsty....\N{\rCHT}渴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.43,1:00:01.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cid!\N{\rCHT}希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.30,1:00:05.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come inside, baby.\N{\rCHT}進去  寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.97,1:00:09.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Who is that man?        - He's just a vagrant.\N{\rCHT}- 那人是誰？    - 是個流浪漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.27,1:00:11.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, he's not.        - Oh, yeah?\N{\rCHT}- 不  他不是    - 是嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.52,1:00:13.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,His shoes are too shiny.\N{\rCHT}他的鞋太亮了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.98,1:00:15.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a smart monkey.\N{\rCHT}真是個聰明的小子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.07,1:00:18.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is he sick?        - Yup.\N{\rCHT}- 他病了嗎？  - 是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.61,1:00:21.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Will he get better?        - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 他會好起來嗎？  - 會的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.20,1:00:25.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Promise?        - Just go to sleep, okay, baby boy?\N{\rCHT}- 你確定？ - 好好睡吧  好嗎  寶貝？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.33,1:00:32.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Night, sweetie.        - Night, Sara.\N{\rCHT}- 晚安  小可愛    - 晚安  薩拉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.33,1:01:10.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey!\N{\rCHT}嘿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.09,1:01:22.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw her face.\N{\rCHT}我第一次見她…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.42,1:01:24.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,First time I saw her face.\N{\rCHT}我第一次見她…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.22,1:01:25.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at me.\N{\rCHT}看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.60,1:01:27.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.01,1:01:30.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw her face.\N{\rCHT}我第一次見她…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.73,1:01:34.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw her face. The first time I saw your face.\N{\rCHT}我第一次見她   我第一次見她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.15,1:01:37.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw her face.\N{\rCHT}我第一次見她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.15,1:02:22.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Morning, monkey. Do you want something to eat?\N{\rCHT}早上好  想吃什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.61,1:02:24.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,The man is up.\N{\rCHT}那人起來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.49,1:02:27.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is he staying here now?\N{\rCHT}他會留在這裡嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.95,1:02:29.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.37,1:02:36.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Toss it.\N{\rCHT}把槍扔了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.00,1:02:40.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm about to finish cleaning it.        - Put it down.\N{\rCHT}- 馬上就擦好了    - 把槍放下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.13,1:02:46.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How are you feeling?        - I'd say I'm at 30 percent.\N{\rCHT}- 你感覺怎麼樣？    - 恢復了三成吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.93,1:02:49.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,You take it slow, by the end of the week you'll be at 50.\N{\rCHT}慢慢來  到週末就能恢復五成了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.72,1:02:55.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,I took you in so you wouldn't die. You're not.\N{\rCHT}我收留你是不想讓你死  既然現在你不會死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.27,1:02:58.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take the morning to rest, then get off my farm.\N{\rCHT}你上午好好休息  然後就走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.27,1:03:00.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I can't do that.        - I'm sorry?\N{\rCHT}- 不行    - 你說什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.40,1:03:02.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need to stay here for a little while.\N{\rCHT}我還要在這裡再呆一陣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.61,1:03:04.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm not cool with that.        - Sorry.\N{\rCHT}- 我不同意    - 我很抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.53,1:03:07.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,You just lost your "take the morning to rest" privileges.\N{\rCHT}你現在連上午在這裡休息的權利都沒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.70,1:03:09.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Get off my farm.        - No.\N{\rCHT}- 現在就給我滾    - 不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.32,1:03:11.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get off my farm.\N{\rCHT}滾出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.49,1:03:14.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,You couldn't scare a retarded hobo with that. Literally.\N{\rCHT}你那玩意兒都嚇不了一個智障  說實話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.58,1:03:17.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a Remington 870. One blast could cut you...\N{\rCHT}這是"雷明頓870"散彈槍  開一槍你就打成…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.50,1:03:19.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,In half. That's telling. You're holding a gun.\N{\rCHT}打成兩半  是啊  你有槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.04,1:03:22.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I say I'm not afraid, so you describe the gun to me.\N{\rCHT}我說了不怕  你還和我說這是什麼槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.09,1:03:24.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not the gun I'm not afraid of.\N{\rCHT}倒不是說我不怕槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.13,1:03:27.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, shoot in the air?\N{\rCHT}你準備幹嘛？對天鳴槍嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.34,1:03:30.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't let me die, you're not gonna kill me.\N{\rCHT}既然你沒見死不救  就不會殺了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.34,1:03:31.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,So that makes me weak?\N{\rCHT}我救你一命反倒要被你要脅了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.05,1:03:35.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not a threat to you or your boy. I need to be on your property.\N{\rCHT}我不想傷害你和你兒子  我只是要呆在這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.72,1:03:39.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd rather there's no contact at all. I'm gonna stay in the fields.\N{\rCHT}但不需要和你們接觸  我就呆在地裡就行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.39,1:03:43.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I need, then you'll never have to deal with me again.\N{\rCHT}只有一件事需要你幫忙  然後咱們就不需要再打交道了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.40,1:03:46.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Verify this is your house in the map so I'm in the right place.\N{\rCHT}你看看地圖上標的是不是你家房子  看我是否找對了地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.28,1:03:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's this?        - It's a map.\N{\rCHT}- 這是什麼？    - 地圖而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.57,1:03:50.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's my house. Why is it marked?\N{\rCHT}這是我家  為什麼被標出來了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.49,1:03:54.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, doesn't matter. Look, I'm gonna be out of the barn in an hour.\N{\rCHT}這不要緊  聽著  我一會就走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.49,1:03:57.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you can spare it, I'm gonna take this canteen.\N{\rCHT}要是你用不著  我就把這個水壺帶走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.37,1:04:01.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is there somewhere I can fill it?        - This number, how did you get this?\N{\rCHT}- 在哪兒能灌水？  - 這個號碼你怎麼會有？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.83,1:04:04.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,That mean something to you?\N{\rCHT}你知道這號碼是什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.55,1:04:08.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? Hey! Hey! Hey!\N{\rCHT}怎麼了？嘿…嘿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.56,1:04:24.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm not a killer.\N{\rCHT}你說得對  我不殺人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.69,1:04:28.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine with how a blast of rock salt to your face won't kill you.\N{\rCHT}但是把石鹽轟到你臉上  我眼都不會眨一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.57,1:04:31.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you're gonna tell me who you are...\N{\rCHT}現在你該告訴我你是誰了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.45,1:04:34.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and what the fuck you're doing on my farm.\N{\rCHT}你他媽到我家裡來幹嘛？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.78,1:04:36.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.45,1:04:41.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Time travel hasn't been invented yet...\N{\rCHT}現在還沒有時間旅行這個說法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.33,1:04:45.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,...but in 30 years, it will have been. It's gonna be used by these criminal...\N{\rCHT}但是三十年後就會有了  它將會被犯罪組織利用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.88,1:04:47.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a looper?\N{\rCHT}你是環形使者？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.10,1:05:02.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't go back to the city because Abe, the boss...\N{\rCHT}我不能回城裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.98,1:05:07.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,...his men will be searching for me 24/7 until they find me. Or find him.\N{\rCHT}我老闆的手下一刻不停在搜城  要把我或他找到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.57,1:05:08.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,All I've got is that map.\N{\rCHT}我手裡只有這張地圖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.36,1:05:12.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,He had three houses marked on it, yours is one of them.\N{\rCHT}上面標了三座房子  你家是其一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.95,1:05:15.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know he's coming here.\N{\rCHT}我知道他會來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.49,1:05:18.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know about loopers? You know what we do?\N{\rCHT}你知道我們是做什麼的嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.95,1:05:22.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,So he's coming here to murder my son...\N{\rCHT}他要到這兒來殺我兒子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.79,1:05:26.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,...because he thinks he might be this Rainmaker?\N{\rCHT}因為他認為他可能是喚雨師？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.04,1:05:29.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Once he kills the Rainmaker, what happens?\N{\rCHT}如果他真殺了喚雨師  會怎麼樣？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.46,1:05:32.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think he thinks if he killed the Rainmaker...\N{\rCHT}我想他覺得如果他真殺了喚雨師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.55,1:05:34.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,...he never would have been sent back.\N{\rCHT}那他就根本不會被送回來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.72,1:05:37.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,He'd just vanish. He'd disappear just like he appeared.\N{\rCHT}他會直接消失  就像他突然出現那樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.26,1:05:41.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,He'd be back with his wife.\N{\rCHT}他和他老婆又能在一起了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.06,1:05:46.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who is he, this guy you let run?\N{\rCHT}被你放跑的那個傢伙是誰？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.27,1:05:48.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just some random guy from the future?\N{\rCHT}只是一個未來的無關緊要的人嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.36,1:05:51.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's just somebody. You know what the numbers mean?\N{\rCHT}他只是個普通人  那到底是什麼號碼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.24,1:06:00.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is Cid's birthday and this is the med code of the hospital he was born in.\N{\rCHT}這是希德的生日  這是他出生的醫院的代碼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.63,1:06:10.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,How many kids were born in that hospital that day with your son?\N{\rCHT}跟你兒子一天在那家醫院出生的小孩還有幾個？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.30,1:06:12.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Like, two?        - Sounds right.\N{\rCHT}- 好像還有兩個吧？    - 估計是了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.21,1:06:15.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Three kids, three houses marked on his map.\N{\rCHT}他把三個孩子的家都標出來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.76,1:06:17.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,One of them is the Rainmaker.\N{\rCHT}他只知道其中有一個就是喚雨師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.43,1:06:20.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- He doesn't know which.        - What's he gonna do?\N{\rCHT}- 但不確定是哪個    - 他會怎麼做？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.56,1:06:23.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.83,1:08:15.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Can he really do this?        - Think about what doing this would fix.\N{\rCHT}- 他真的會下手嗎？  - 你想想他這樣做能改變什麼吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.17,1:08:18.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,What he thinks it would fix.\N{\rCHT}他以為能改變什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.34,1:08:25.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,If he comes here, will you stop him?\N{\rCHT}如果他真來了  你會阻止他嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.06,1:08:31.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm asking, can I trust you?        - I don't care if you trust me.\N{\rCHT}- 我是在問  我能不能信你？   - 我不管你是否相信我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.39,1:08:33.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't care about your son.\N{\rCHT}也不管你兒子死活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.56,1:08:36.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I lost my life. I kill this man, I get it back.\N{\rCHT}我殺了他  我自己就能活命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.45,1:08:45.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,He'll kill the other two kids and come here last. Put off facing me.\N{\rCHT}他會先殺了其他兩個孩子之後再過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.58,1:08:49.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,All this goddamn cane leaves us blind.\N{\rCHT}有這些甘蔗擋著  我們什麼都看不見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.50,1:08:53.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,He can get within 50 yards of this place without a hawk spotting him.\N{\rCHT}他可以躲在裡面  誰都發現不了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.46,1:08:56.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,What makes sense is we burn the fields. Level them.\N{\rCHT}我們應該把地燒了  把雜草鏟平{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.00,1:08:59.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,How much gas you got in that barn?\N{\rCHT}你倉庫裡有多少汽油？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.76,1:09:03.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, you can't burn down my cane fields.        - This stuff is half dead anyway.\N{\rCHT}- 不行  不能燒甘蔗地   - 它們已死得差不多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.84,1:09:09.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the seed for next year. It's not gonna happen, you fucking nut.\N{\rCHT}但是要留著為來年做種  不能燒  絕對不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.06,1:09:17.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, use what you need and set up anywhere.\N{\rCHT}聽著  你需要什麼儘管拿  都聽你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.61,1:09:20.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,But one thing: I don't want you talking to Cid.\N{\rCHT}但有一條：別和我兒子說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.36,1:09:22.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I watch my son, you watch the cane.\N{\rCHT}我看好我兒子  你看好甘蔗地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.45,1:09:24.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's the deal.        - Good by me.\N{\rCHT}- 就這麼著吧     - 我沒問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.20,1:09:25.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fine.\N{\rCHT}那就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.78,1:09:28.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jesus.        - All right, hold still.\N{\rCHT}- 天呐    - 行了  別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.95,1:09:33.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's easy for things to get infected on a farm.\N{\rCHT}在農場受傷很容易感染…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.33,1:09:34.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Start falling off.\N{\rCHT}傷口縫好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.42,1:09:39.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pussy.\N{\rCHT}娘娘腔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.88,1:09:45.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm out here and you're in the house. We need a way to communicate.\N{\rCHT}我在外面  你在屋子裡  我們需要一種聯繫方式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.55,1:09:49.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a dinner bell in the barn. You can ring that if someone's coming.\N{\rCHT}在倉庫裡有個晚飯鈴  如果有人來了  你就按鈴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.68,1:09:53.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dinner bell. We need buzzers or walkies or something.\N{\rCHT}我們要的是蜂鳴器或對講機之類的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.64,1:09:57.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we've got, but I'll look. Cid!\N{\rCHT}不知道有沒有  我來找找  希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.28,1:10:02.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How's the math coming?        - I want to help the man.\N{\rCHT}- 算術做得怎麼樣？  - 我想幫那個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.03,1:10:05.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Help him with what?        - I could help him with my toys.\N{\rCHT}- 用什麼幫他？   - 用我的玩具{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.03,1:10:07.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. Let me talk to you.\N{\rCHT}不可以  聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.78,1:10:11.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need you to stay away from that man. Okay?\N{\rCHT}你離那個人遠點  明白嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.49,1:10:13.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let him do his thing, but stick with me.\N{\rCHT}他做他的  你就呆在我身邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.79,1:10:16.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Okay?        - Is he not good?\N{\rCHT}- 明白嗎？ - 他不是好人嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.58,1:10:19.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we're gonna see what he is. All right?\N{\rCHT}我們要看看他是什麼人   好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.29,1:10:21.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I need you to stick with me.\N{\rCHT}跟我呆一起就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.67,1:10:23.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good boy.\N{\rCHT}好孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.60,1:11:13.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hand me that Phillips.\N{\rCHT}把那個夾子給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.94,1:11:21.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Tell me if you hear her coming.        - What are we doing here?\N{\rCHT}- 要是聽到她來了就告訴我    - 我們這是幹嘛？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.40,1:11:23.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Commundication.\N{\rCHT}做信號器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.07,1:11:28.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I need to make it stronger.\N{\rCHT}這個信號還要加強{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.86,1:11:31.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And how do we do that?        - Bigger battery.\N{\rCHT}- 要怎麼弄？ - 用大點的電池{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.66,1:11:33.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Smart.\N{\rCHT}聰明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.83,1:11:38.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you kill people?\N{\rCHT}你會殺人嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.88,1:11:45.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's say I kill people.\N{\rCHT}算會吧…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.46,1:11:47.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,With your gun?\N{\rCHT}用你的槍？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.51,1:11:53.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You want a gun like mine?        - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 你也想要一把我這樣的槍？ - 嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.76,1:11:57.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with it, pole vaulting? It's bigger than you.\N{\rCHT}你要槍做什麼？撐杆跳？槍比你還大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.31,1:12:02.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop bad things from happening.\N{\rCHT}阻止壞的事情發生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.15,1:12:05.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit!\N{\rCHT}媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.58,1:12:23.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,So how long you and your mom been out here on the farm?\N{\rCHT}你和你媽媽在這兒住多久了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.00,1:12:25.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's not.\N{\rCHT}她不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.42,1:12:28.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's not what?\N{\rCHT}不是什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.09,1:12:33.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sara doesn't know, but I remember my real mom.\N{\rCHT}薩拉不知道  但我記得我真正的媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.72,1:12:39.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,When I was a baby, I couldn't stop it.\N{\rCHT}我那時候很小  我無能為力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.14,1:12:42.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Couldn't stop what?\N{\rCHT}對什麼無能為力？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.19,1:12:46.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop her from getting killed.\N{\rCHT}阻止我媽媽被殺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.61,1:12:50.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,I saw it, but I couldn't stop it.\N{\rCHT}我看見了  但是我阻止不了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.61,1:12:53.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wasn't strong enough.\N{\rCHT}我不夠強大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.83,1:12:57.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should....\N{\rCHT}你應該…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.91,1:13:03.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You should talk to your mom about this.        - She's not my mom. She's a liar.\N{\rCHT}- 你應該和你媽媽談談這個    - 她不是我媽媽  她是騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.76,1:13:22.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Spotted him coming out of a sewer tunnel on the west end. He's on the run.\N{\rCHT}我們發現他從西區的下水道裡出來   正在逃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.16,1:13:36.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Think he's heading to the west on Talbott Street...\N{\rCHT}他在往西塔街跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.99,1:13:40.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,...possibly to Whore's Alley. We have a visual.\N{\rCHT}好像是去紅燈區{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.87,1:13:45.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't take that thing out with a plow or something?\N{\rCHT}你不能用犁把那樹根拉掉嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.96,1:13:52.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, I found a....\N{\rCHT}聽著  我找到…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.76,1:13:56.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,In the barn, I found some parts and I made a thing.\N{\rCHT}我在倉庫裡找到一些零件  做了個東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.55,1:13:59.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here.\N{\rCHT}給{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.31,1:14:04.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,So if you see something, just push that.\N{\rCHT}如果你看到什麼  就按一下那個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.81,1:14:07.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,When?\N{\rCHT}什麼時候的事？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.40,1:14:13.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Last night he woke me up. Don't tell him I told you. He didn't...\N{\rCHT}昨晚他過來喊我的  別說是我說的  我答應他不告訴你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.95,1:14:19.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,You said you were his mom.\N{\rCHT}你說你是他媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.49,1:14:22.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.62,1:14:25.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,He told me you're not.\N{\rCHT}他跟我說你不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.87,1:14:28.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,He said that?\N{\rCHT}他說的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.34,1:14:31.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.59,1:14:36.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- If he's not your son, who is he?           - He's my son.\N{\rCHT}- 如果他不是你兒子  那他是誰？ - 他是我兒子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.14,1:14:40.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I had Cid when I was 22.\N{\rCHT}我22歲時生的他…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.97,1:14:43.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want to give up my life in the city.\N{\rCHT}但我不想放棄市里的生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.77,1:14:47.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I dropped him here on the farm with my sister...\N{\rCHT}所以我把他留在這農場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.73,1:14:51.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,...and she saw how I was living, so she took him.\N{\rCHT}我姐姐看到我當時的生活狀況  就把他接了過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.65,1:14:54.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,And my sister, she raised him.\N{\rCHT}然後我姐姐撫養了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.16,1:15:00.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,She loved him. He called her Mom.\N{\rCHT}她愛他  他叫她媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.50,1:15:09.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,How did she get killed?\N{\rCHT}她是怎麼死的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.38,1:15:10.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ.\N{\rCHT}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.67,1:15:12.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,He remembers it. You've gotta talk to him.\N{\rCHT}他都記得  你真應該和他好好談談{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.00,1:15:16.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told you one thing. I told you to stay away from my son.\N{\rCHT}我告訴過你  離我兒子遠點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.63,1:15:19.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- He asked about my gun.        - Stay out of it!\N{\rCHT}- 他問了我槍的事    - 你別管就行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.34,1:15:21.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,And stay the fuck away from my son!\N{\rCHT}你他媽離我兒子遠點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.43,1:15:28.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where does 56 go?\N{\rCHT}56應該放哪裡？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.60,1:15:32.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. You're smart.\N{\rCHT}乖  真聰明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.61,1:15:33.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Twenty-one?\N{\rCHT}那21呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.82,1:15:35.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,How long can you not sleep?\N{\rCHT}你能多長時間不睡覺？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.15,1:15:39.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Probably a while. It's a good question.\N{\rCHT}不知道…可能就一會兒吧  這個問題很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.11,1:15:42.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where does it go? Come on.\N{\rCHT}該放哪兒？快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.37,1:15:45.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.00,1:15:47.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thirty-two?\N{\rCHT}到32了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.58,1:15:50.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You should help Joe watch.        - Joe?\N{\rCHT}- 我們應該幫喬一起守著   - 喬？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.75,1:15:53.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because he can't stay awake all the time.\N{\rCHT}因為他不可能一直不睡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.17,1:15:55.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Isn't our business. Okay?         - He's keeping us safe.\N{\rCHT}- 這跟我們沒關係  知道嗎？ - 他在保護我們的安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.96,1:15:57.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's do this now, okay?\N{\rCHT}現在我們專心做這個  好嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.80,1:16:00.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have 32 there. I know you know this one.\N{\rCHT}你手上拿著32  你肯定知道該放哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.72,1:16:07.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No. Eight times three is what?        - Thirty-two.\N{\rCHT}- 不對  8乘以3等於幾？   - 32{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.23,1:16:09.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Eight times three is what?\N{\rCHT}8乘以3等於幾？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.44,1:16:10.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,32{\r}\N{\fs18\fnCronos Pro Subhead}Thirty-two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.15,1:16:19.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want you to count three eights.        - Eight, sixteen...\N{\rCHT}- 你來數3個8      - 8, 16…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.99,1:16:22.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,32{\r}\N{\fs18\fnCronos Pro Subhead}Thirty-two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.20,1:16:24.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You telling me you want alone time?        - No.\N{\rCHT}- 你是不是想一個人呆著了？ - 不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.58,1:16:27.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you put that where it belongs?\N{\rCHT}那你為什麼不放到對的地方呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.29,1:16:35.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Alone time.        - He's protecting us...\N{\rCHT}- 一個人呆著吧   - 他在保護我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.34,1:16:37.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,...because you can't do it.\N{\rCHT}因為你做不到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.30,1:16:40.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I told you to stay away from him, didn't I?        - I never did anything.\N{\rCHT}- 我告訴過你離他遠點    - 我什麼也沒做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.01,1:16:42.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Do you think I'm stupid?        - So?\N{\rCHT}- 你覺得我蠢麼？    - 那又怎樣？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.93,1:16:45.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I told Joe to leave...        - So?\N{\rCHT}- 我告訴過你…   - 那又怎樣？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.68,1:16:48.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You do what I tell you!        - You can't tell me what to do.\N{\rCHT}- 你要按我說的做     - 你沒資格命令我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.68,1:16:50.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not my mom!\N{\rCHT}你不是我媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.27,1:16:52.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not my mom! You're a liar!\N{\rCHT}你不是我媽媽  你這個騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.44,1:16:55.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get killed because you won't stop lying!\N{\rCHT}你也會被殺掉  因為你騙人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.36,1:16:57.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Cid, calm down.        - You're lying! I hate you!\N{\rCHT}- 希德  冷靜…    - 你騙我  我恨你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.90,1:17:00.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You're lying to me! I hate you!        - Cid....\N{\rCHT}- 你騙我  我恨你   - 希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.19,1:17:03.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I hate you! Liar! You're lying!        - Calm down. Calm down.\N{\rCHT}- 我恨你  騙子  你騙我…   - 冷靜  冷靜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.63,1:17:24.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Liar!\N{\rCHT}騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.64,1:17:28.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not my mom! You're a liar!\N{\rCHT}你不是我媽媽  你是騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.81,1:17:35.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not my mom!\N{\rCHT}你不是我媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.69,1:17:36.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hate you!\N{\rCHT}我恨你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.06,1:17:38.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Liar!\N{\rCHT}騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.73,1:17:41.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Liar! Liar!\N{\rCHT}騙子  騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.35,1:18:16.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.98,1:18:21.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay, sweetie.\N{\rCHT}沒事了  親愛的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.99,1:19:09.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy shit.\N{\rCHT}我操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.00,1:20:04.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Evening, ma'am.\N{\rCHT}你好  夫人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.50,1:20:08.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Evening. How can I help you?\N{\rCHT}你好  有事嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.76,1:20:13.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can start by accepting my apologies re the hour.\N{\rCHT}抱歉這麼晚來訪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.39,1:20:15.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hope I didn't catch you at supper.        - That's fine.\N{\rCHT}- 希望沒有打擾到你們的晚餐   - 沒事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.10,1:20:18.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been walking between empty farms all day.\N{\rCHT}我在太陽下走訪了好幾個空農場了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.81,1:20:21.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd just tick this one off the list.\N{\rCHT}我想今天把您家一併結束了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.31,1:20:24.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Not have to come back tomorrow.        - What's this about?\N{\rCHT}- 這樣明天就不用來了    - 結束什麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.90,1:20:26.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You alone here, ma'am?\N{\rCHT}你不是一個人在這兒住吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.98,1:20:28.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,My husband should be back any time.\N{\rCHT}我丈夫很快會從城裡回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.03,1:20:30.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Happy to hear it.\N{\rCHT}那就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.03,1:20:36.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Could I trouble you for some water?\N{\rCHT}能麻煩藉口水喝麼？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.70,1:20:39.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some. You can take the glass with you.\N{\rCHT}我去給你倒點  杯子你就直接帶走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.91,1:20:41.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Actually, ma'am...\N{\rCHT}抱歉  夫人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.87,1:20:45.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,...my business today, this ticking off the list business...\N{\rCHT}我今天來是為了走訪表單上的人家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.70,1:20:48.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,is gonna require me coming in,\N{\rCHT}必須得進屋子看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.13,1:20:49.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,if that's all right.\N{\rCHT}如果您不介意的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.63,1:20:52.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Will you tell me what this is about?        - I will, yes.\N{\rCHT}- 能告訴我到底是什麼事呢？ - 一定跟您說明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.76,1:20:57.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I come in?\N{\rCHT}我能先進去嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.85,1:21:02.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ma'am?\N{\rCHT}夫人？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.86,1:21:14.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm a deputized police officer, looking for an escaped criminal.\N{\rCHT}我是員警  正在這片搜捕逃犯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.32,1:21:18.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyone through here in the past two days, vagrants?\N{\rCHT}這兩天有沒有在附近見過可疑人士？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.54,1:21:21.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Vagrants are always passing, nobody near the house.\N{\rCHT}這附近總有流浪漢四處遊蕩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.37,1:21:22.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,That man there?\N{\rCHT}這個人有見過嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.50,1:21:25.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's young. No.\N{\rCHT}他很年輕啊  沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.71,1:21:29.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're looking for his father, too. Similar looking build, late 50s...\N{\rCHT}我們也在找他的父親  他們長得很像  快60了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.67,1:21:32.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,...may or may not be traveling together.\N{\rCHT}他們兩個可能在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.18,1:21:35.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize them?\N{\rCHT}見過嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.26,1:21:39.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No.        - Keep them.\N{\rCHT}- 沒有   - 照片你留著吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.81,1:21:43.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your kids with your husband?\N{\rCHT}你孩子們和你先生在一起？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.65,1:21:47.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just one.\N{\rCHT}是  我只有一個孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.27,1:21:49.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How old?        - Ten.\N{\rCHT}- 多大了？  - 十歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.86,1:21:51.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ten....\N{\rCHT}十歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.80,1:22:13.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show you the barn and house.\N{\rCHT}我帶你去倉庫看看  然後再來這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.92,1:22:15.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then you can be on your way.\N{\rCHT}然後你就可以交差了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.01,1:22:19.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I took the liberty with your barn. Apologies.\N{\rCHT}倉庫我已經看過了  抱歉沒先打聲招呼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.93,1:22:23.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the house.\N{\rCHT}現在只要看房子就行了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.87,1:22:41.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Ten, you said? Your boy?        - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 你說你兒子10歲？    - 是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.54,1:22:43.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,And your husband?\N{\rCHT}你丈夫呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.33,1:22:47.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've just gotta check in with the home office.\N{\rCHT}我把資訊傳回總部核實一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.34,1:22:52.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,The boy's in the city with his father. When they getting back?\N{\rCHT}你說孩子和父親都在城裡  他們什麼時候回來？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.76,1:22:54.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Couldn't tell you.\N{\rCHT}不好說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.64,1:23:02.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,This goddamn thing.\N{\rCHT}破玩意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.77,1:23:05.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can never get a signal this far out of town.\N{\rCHT}離城遠了就沒信號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.23,1:23:10.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Piece of shit.\N{\rCHT}垃圾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.65,1:23:17.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here we go.\N{\rCHT}總算連上了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.86,1:23:20.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is this man dangerous?\N{\rCHT}這人很危險嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.62,1:23:24.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,He shoots men down for a living. He's a stone-cold killer.\N{\rCHT}他以殺人為生  是個冷血殺手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.66,1:23:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,My boss has half the city looking for him.\N{\rCHT}我老大傾半城人力在找他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.96,1:23:30.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Half the city and me, so....\N{\rCHT}半城人力  加上我…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.58,1:23:33.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,And if you find him, there's a hell of a price.\N{\rCHT}如果你發現他了  能有很可觀的獎金哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.21,1:23:36.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Chunk of money like that, you should think on it.\N{\rCHT}一大筆錢  你考慮一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.92,1:23:41.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I will.        - All right. Show me upstairs.\N{\rCHT}- 我會的    - 好  帶我上樓看看？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.81,1:23:45.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's drafts in the house.\N{\rCHT}房子裡老是有穿堂風{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.99,1:24:08.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,My granddad built this tunnel when the vagrant raids got bad.\N{\rCHT}流浪漢鬧得厲害的時候  我爺爺挖了這條地道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.04,1:24:12.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Nana said he was nuts.        - Thank you, Granddad.\N{\rCHT}- 奶奶說他瘋了   - 多虧了你爺爺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.38,1:24:16.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That wasn't the man.        - No. It's funny. I know that guy, though.\N{\rCHT}- 他不是那個要殺我們的壞蛋吧？ - 不是  我還算認識他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.92,1:24:21.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,His name is Jesse. I like him. He's good.\N{\rCHT}他叫傑西  我喜歡他  他人挺好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.93,1:24:24.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's gonna go away once he doesn't find me.\N{\rCHT}如果他找不到我  他就會走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.64,1:24:26.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,He won't hurt your mom.\N{\rCHT}他不會傷害你媽媽…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.02,1:24:29.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sara.        - Where's your mom?\N{\rCHT}- 我是說薩拉    - 你媽媽呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.65,1:24:33.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where's my mom?\N{\rCHT}我媽媽呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.32,1:24:40.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,She gave me up. I was younger than you.\N{\rCHT}她把我賣了  那時我比你還小{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.16,1:24:45.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,We were vagrants, and she was alone.\N{\rCHT}賣給了流浪漢  她那時候孤身一人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.24,1:24:50.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought she was stupid for getting on the drugs she was on...\N{\rCHT}以前  我老覺得她太蠢了  一直吸毒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.71,1:24:54.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,...but now I see she was just so alone.\N{\rCHT}但我現在懂了  她只是太孤單了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.13,1:24:56.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's what she had.\N{\rCHT}她一無所有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.09,1:25:00.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,She sold me to a panhandle gang.\N{\rCHT}於是把我賣給了一個丐幫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.84,1:25:05.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got away and I ran and ended up on this train.\N{\rCHT}我逃了出來  跑啊跑  最後跳上一輛火車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.26,1:25:07.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,I remember I was sitting there in an empty car.\N{\rCHT}我記得我坐在空蕩蕩的車廂裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.47,1:25:10.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I saw myself over and over again...\N{\rCHT}我一遍遍地想像自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.64,1:25:12.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,...killing those men that bought me,\N{\rCHT}殺掉那些買下我的傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.89,1:25:15.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,that got my mom on what she was on.\N{\rCHT}還有那些讓我媽媽生不如死的傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.56,1:25:19.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just finding them and tearing them apart. Saving my mom.\N{\rCHT}找到他們  把他們撕成碎片  救出我媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.69,1:25:20.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you didn't.\N{\rCHT}但是你沒這樣做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.24,1:25:24.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, a man in the city found me, put a gun in my hand.\N{\rCHT}城裡有個人發現了我  給了我一把槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.16,1:25:27.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gave me something that was mine.\N{\rCHT}給了我一些本屬於我的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.29,1:25:31.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's just men trying to figure out what they would do...\N{\rCHT}世上有種人  他們知道該做什麼…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.46,1:25:33.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,...to keep what's theirs, what they've got.\N{\rCHT}才能保護好他們的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.46,1:25:36.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the only kind of man there is.\N{\rCHT}要做就做這樣的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.04,1:25:40.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let Sara get killed.\N{\rCHT}我不會讓薩拉被殺的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.43,1:25:53.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think we're clear.\N{\rCHT}我們安全了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.70,1:26:06.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sara!\N{\rCHT}莎拉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.79,1:26:11.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Baby.\N{\rCHT}寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.22,1:26:31.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,All working girls, yeah?\N{\rCHT}這片都是夜店的妞  對嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.72,1:26:35.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,This whole block and a couple of blocks over.\N{\rCHT}這整個街區  還有那邊的幾塊都是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.15,1:26:38.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, Joe.\N{\rCHT}你好啊  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.48,1:26:41.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you want to check those, too, I can arrange.\N{\rCHT}那些也要看看嗎  我可以安排{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.70,1:26:47.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm an arranger, stranger.\N{\rCHT}我辦事你放心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.99,1:26:50.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you don't see what you want to see, no refunds.\N{\rCHT}不過就算你沒找到要找的  錢也不能退{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.22,1:27:56.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.77,1:28:00.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,What happened?\N{\rCHT}出什麼事了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.69,1:28:49.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's pretty good.\N{\rCHT}挺厲害啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.57,1:28:54.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,In the city, young guys would...\N{\rCHT}在城裡  那些男人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.32,1:28:58.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,...hit on me by floating fucking quarters.\N{\rCHT}想把硬幣弄浮起來  跟我搭訕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.79,1:29:02.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't tell them I was TK...\N{\rCHT}我不說我也是念力者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.21,1:29:04.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,...but I would keep their quarters down.\N{\rCHT}但是我會讓他們的硬幣浮不起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.25,1:29:10.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,This one guy just busted a blood vessel in his eye trying to get it up.\N{\rCHT}有個傢伙  眼睛的血管都爆了  也沒讓硬幣漂起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.90,1:29:25.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's you.\N{\rCHT}那個人就是你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.02,1:29:27.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your loop.\N{\rCHT}他就是你的環{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.19,1:29:31.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,You lied to me.\N{\rCHT}你對我撒謊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.74,1:29:36.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I know you're not lying when you say you're gonna kill this guy...\N{\rCHT}不過我相信你沒說謊  當你說要殺了這人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.74,1:29:38.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,...your own self.\N{\rCHT}也就是殺你自己的時候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.99,1:29:42.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,You protected Cid from that gat man.\N{\rCHT}那個槍手在的時候  你保護了希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.10,1:29:44.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,- come on.       - He... \N{\rCHT}- 別說了   - 其實{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.63,1:29:47.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.        - He saved your ass, didn't he?\N{\rCHT}- 對    - 是他救了你的命  是嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.71,1:29:49.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,He saved my ass.\N{\rCHT}是他救了我的命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.92,1:29:51.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's a....\N{\rCHT}他是個…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.59,1:29:56.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's a good kid.\N{\rCHT}他是個好孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.43,1:29:58.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he is.\N{\rCHT}是的  他很乖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.10,1:30:05.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, when I came back, after my sister died...\N{\rCHT}我回來的時候  就是我姐死了之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.27,1:30:08.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,...I remember seeing him...\N{\rCHT}我記得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.86,1:30:14.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,...for the first time in two years just sitting on the porch.\N{\rCHT}兩年來第一次見到他  他就坐在門廊下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.91,1:30:19.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,I drove up crying. I'd been at this...\N{\rCHT}我哭著開著車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.62,1:30:23.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,...party all night in the city when I got the call...\N{\rCHT}我剛剛結束在城裡的一個派對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.42,1:30:31.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,...so I was wearing this ridiculous party dress.\N{\rCHT}還沒來得及換衣服{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.38,1:30:36.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,All my ridiculous shit.\N{\rCHT}我看上去可笑極了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.05,1:30:40.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I don't know if he...\N{\rCHT}我不知道…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.52,1:30:44.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,...even remembered me...\N{\rCHT}不知道他是否還記得我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.52,1:30:47.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,...but he looked at me....\N{\rCHT}但是他看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.11,1:30:56.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,I abandoned him.\N{\rCHT}我拋棄了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.95,1:31:02.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I abandoned my baby.\N{\rCHT}我拋棄了我的孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.33,1:31:10.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I've seen so many men in the city...\N{\rCHT}在城裡我見過太多的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.63,1:31:15.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,...who I look in their eyes and they're just lost.\N{\rCHT}他們的眼神都是空洞的  眼裡只有迷茫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.76,1:31:20.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,So whether he loves me back or not...\N{\rCHT}所以不管他愛不愛我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.22,1:31:25.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,...as long as I'm there to raise him...\N{\rCHT}只要我還活著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.85,1:31:29.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,...he's gonna be taken care of.\N{\rCHT}我就要好好照顧他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.90,1:31:33.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's gonna be safe.\N{\rCHT}我要保護他的安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.32,1:31:38.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's never gonna get lost.\N{\rCHT}他永遠也不會迷茫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.39,1:32:02.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, Joe.\N{\rCHT}你好啊  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.26,1:32:04.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesse.\N{\rCHT}傑西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.06,1:32:09.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put this down and let her go.\N{\rCHT}我把槍放下  你放開她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.73,1:32:14.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sara, Jesse here is the best shot with a gat that I know.\N{\rCHT}薩拉  傑西是我認識的人裡槍法最好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.07,1:32:18.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,When he lets you go, just sit on the couch. Don't do anything stupid.\N{\rCHT}他放開你後  你就坐下  別做傻事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.66,1:32:27.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's coming here, Jess. My loop is coming here.\N{\rCHT}他要來了  傑西  我的環要來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.75,1:32:31.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I gotta take you in.        - I got 948 bars of pure silver.\N{\rCHT}- 我必須得抓你回去    - 我有948塊純銀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.79,1:32:33.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I close my loop, I get right with Abe.\N{\rCHT}我會封了我的環  回去找亞伯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.96,1:32:36.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whatever he gives back, I'll split it with you.\N{\rCHT}不管他還給我多少  我分你一半{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.59,1:32:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Was that your plan?\N{\rCHT}就這樣而已嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.26,1:32:40.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, take all of it.\N{\rCHT}好吧  我全都給你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.55,1:32:43.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you delusional? You ain't getting right.\N{\rCHT}別犯傻了  沒人會幫你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.39,1:32:47.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Long as Abe's got one gat man standing he's gonna hunt you until his dying day.\N{\rCHT}只要亞伯還剩一個槍手  到死他都不會放過你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.60,1:32:52.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go now. Gonna get in my truck and you're just gonna....\N{\rCHT}我們還是走吧  坐上我的卡車  這就走…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.12,1:33:08.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.47,1:34:12.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Rainmaker....\N{\rCHT}喚雨師…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.29,1:34:39.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cid!\N{\rCHT}希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.63,1:34:42.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God!\N{\rCHT}老天…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.26,1:34:47.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cid!\N{\rCHT}希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.22,1:34:50.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cid?\N{\rCHT}希德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.51,1:34:55.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's him. What is he, some TK freak?\N{\rCHT}就是他  他是超強念力者嗎？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.89,1:34:57.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,You knew.\N{\rCHT}你早就知道了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.98,1:35:02.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing?        - How did your sister die?\N{\rCHT}- 你要幹嘛？ - 你姐姐怎麼死的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.53,1:35:06.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing with those guns?        - How's she die? Is that what happened to her?\N{\rCHT}- 你拿著槍要幹嘛？ - 她是不是也像剛才那樣死的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.20,1:35:07.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No!        - He kill her like that?\N{\rCHT}- 不   - 他就像那樣殺了她？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.91,1:35:11.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. He was climbing a bookshelf and it fell back on him.\N{\rCHT}他當時在爬書架  書架倒下來壓住了他…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.45,1:35:13.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,He can get scared. It exploded.\N{\rCHT}他嚇壞了  於是就爆發了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.08,1:35:16.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jesus frigging...        - He'll learn to control it.\N{\rCHT}-  天哪    - 但總有一天他會控制的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.62,1:35:20.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Imagine what he's gonna do!        - If he did good with it, though.\N{\rCHT}- 想想他能造什麼孽吧   - 但是他也可能用它來做好事啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.67,1:35:23.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,If he grew up with me raising him.\N{\rCHT}如果他長大  控制能力也會變強吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.71,1:35:26.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,If he grew up good....\N{\rCHT}如果他長大以後是個好人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.38,1:35:28.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,He doesn't.\N{\rCHT}事實證明他不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.14,1:35:31.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,You stay away from him, Joe!\N{\rCHT}你別動他  喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.18,1:35:40.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cid! Stay away from Joe, baby!\N{\rCHT}希德  離喬遠點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.81,1:35:42.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Follow me, baby!\N{\rCHT}聽話  寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.79,1:36:44.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come to me. It's okay.\N{\rCHT}過來  沒事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.72,1:36:51.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby.\N{\rCHT}沒事了  寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.85,1:36:55.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right now two things have happened.\N{\rCHT}現在有兩件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.85,1:36:58.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,My loop knows Cid's the kid he's looking for.\N{\rCHT}那個人已經知道希德就是他要找的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.35,1:37:00.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,And my gang knows I'm here.\N{\rCHT}還有我老闆也知道我在這裡了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.27,1:37:04.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,That means in 15 minutes, one or both of them is coming down that highway.\N{\rCHT}也就是說  不出一刻鐘  一方或雙方就會從那條公路上過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.73,1:37:07.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pack up the truck. Take everything you can and go.\N{\rCHT}你收拾好東西  開那個槍手的車趕快走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.61,1:37:10.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Drive north away from the city.\N{\rCHT}一路向北  離開這兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.78,1:37:12.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.21,1:37:27.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got everyone here, all our men.\N{\rCHT}所有人都到齊了  集合完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.38,1:37:29.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Arm them up. Let's go.\N{\rCHT}全副武裝  立刻出發{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.22,1:37:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got him, Abe. I got him.\N{\rCHT}我抓到他了  亞伯  我抓到他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.10,1:37:43.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, shit.\N{\rCHT}真他媽巧…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.06,1:37:47.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's right, motherfuckers.\N{\rCHT}兔崽子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.11,1:37:50.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got him.\N{\rCHT}我抓到他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.69,1:37:52.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Knew he was sweet on this one whore.\N{\rCHT}他和一個妓女有一腿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.82,1:37:55.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I checked her building...        - They found Joe...\N{\rCHT}- 我查了她住的樓…    - 他們也找到喬了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.28,1:37:58.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,...in a farm on the east side. That's why all the gat men are here.\N{\rCHT}在東邊的一個農場裡  這就是為什麼所有人都集合了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.08,1:38:02.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,The whole crew is arming up to make a sweep.\N{\rCHT}所有人都全副武裝  要掃平那裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.21,1:38:03.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Joe?\N{\rCHT}喬？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.71,1:38:06.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fuck Joe. Save your bullets! I've got the loop!\N{\rCHT}去他媽的喬  省省子彈吧  我抓到了他的環…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.38,1:38:11.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not such a fuck-up now, huh? I'm bringing him up to see Abe.\N{\rCHT}現在到底是誰他媽慫了  我帶他去見亞伯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.39,1:38:22.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get this asshole!\N{\rCHT}來呀  混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.35,1:38:26.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Motherfuckers!\N{\rCHT}去你媽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.80,1:39:40.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy shit.\N{\rCHT}我操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.69,1:39:49.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Joe!\N{\rCHT}喬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.23,1:39:54.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Guess I put the gun in that kid's hand, huh?\N{\rCHT}當年還是我教的那孩子用槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.20,1:40:00.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess everything comes back around.\N{\rCHT}這就是現世報吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.70,1:40:04.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like your goddamn ties.\N{\rCHT}就像你那該死的領帶…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.37,1:41:31.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take this truck. And take your gold and go live your life.\N{\rCHT}這車給你  帶上錢  想去哪就去哪吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.96,1:41:35.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody's coming after you. I fixed it.\N{\rCHT}沒人會追殺你了  我都擺平了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.84,1:41:38.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,You go kill the boy. That how you fix it?\N{\rCHT}你是要殺了那孩子嗎？來擺平一切？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.25,1:41:40.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're goddamn right I'm gonna kill that boy!\N{\rCHT}你他媽說對了  我要殺了那兔崽子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.01,1:41:44.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You just got your life back.        - My life?\N{\rCHT}- 我給你撿了一條命   - 我的命？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.22,1:41:47.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your life. Becoming you.\N{\rCHT}是你的命吧  好讓我變成你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.18,1:41:50.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goddamn it! You've lost your fucking mind!\N{\rCHT}你他媽瘋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.18,1:41:54.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You let this boy live, he's going to take everything you've got.\N{\rCHT}你現在放那孩子一馬  將來他會讓你一無所有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.19,1:41:56.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,And everything I got!\N{\rCHT}讓我一無所有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.06,1:41:58.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,See what he becomes.\N{\rCHT}你已經知道他以後會變成什麼樣的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.43,1:42:00.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen that yet.\N{\rCHT}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.54,1:42:54.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.75,1:42:57.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, baby, we're going.\N{\rCHT}好了  寶貝  我們走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.92,1:43:00.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put your seat belt on.\N{\rCHT}系好安全帶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.20,1:43:28.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Stop.        - Duck down. It's okay.\N{\rCHT}- 停車    - 臥倒  沒事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.07,1:43:31.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Stop, please. He can shoot us.        - Duck down.\N{\rCHT}- 快停車  他要開槍了    - 臥倒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.87,1:43:35.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!\N{\rCHT}停車 停車 停車 停車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.06,1:43:59.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Cid.        - I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}- 希德…    - 對不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.65,1:44:03.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay. I'm gonna get you down.\N{\rCHT}沒事  沒事  我把你解開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.99,1:44:15.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going into the cane. Go. Go.\N{\rCHT}快躲到甘蔗地裡去  快跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.75,1:44:23.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go.\N{\rCHT}跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.27,1:44:42.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,No!\N{\rCHT}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.57,1:44:53.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. Cid, no.\N{\rCHT}不  希德  不要…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.96,1:45:43.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,No!\N{\rCHT}不…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.59,1:45:52.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby. You're okay.\N{\rCHT}沒事了  寶貝  沒事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.76,1:45:56.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay, baby.\N{\rCHT}沒事了  寶貝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.68,1:46:02.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay.\N{\rCHT}沒事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.94,1:46:05.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you. Calm down.\N{\rCHT}我愛你  冷靜下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.56,1:46:08.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good boy.\N{\rCHT}乖孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.61,1:46:18.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mommy loves you.\N{\rCHT}媽媽愛你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.37,1:46:21.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's okay.\N{\rCHT}沒事了…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.58,1:46:25.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mom.\N{\rCHT}媽媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.18,1:46:36.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit.\N{\rCHT}操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.01,1:46:43.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,You did good. You did so good. Good boy.\N{\rCHT}你做得很好  做得很好  好孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.81,1:46:49.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. I need you to run into the fields now.\N{\rCHT}聽我說  你先到地裡去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.07,1:46:53.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, Mom, I don't want to leave you.        - It's okay.\N{\rCHT}- 不  媽媽  我不要離開你    - 沒事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.90,1:46:56.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You need to go. Go!        - Move!\N{\rCHT}- 你該走了     - 閃開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.32,1:46:58.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move, goddamn it!\N{\rCHT}你他媽閃開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.13,1:47:16.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Move.\N{\rCHT}閃開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.18,1:47:23.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then I saw it.\N{\rCHT}眼前的一切突然讓我明白了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.94,1:47:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I saw a mom who would die for her son.\N{\rCHT}一位母親為了兒子甘願死去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.61,1:47:35.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,A man who would kill for his wife.\N{\rCHT}一個男人為了救回妻子不惜殺人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.91,1:47:40.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,A boy, angry and alone.\N{\rCHT}一個孩子因此變得扭曲而孤獨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.33,1:47:44.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Laid out in front of him, the bad path. I saw it.\N{\rCHT}我看見那條毀滅之路就在他面前出現{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.62,1:47:49.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,And the path was a circle...\N{\rCHT}這條路循環往復{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.88,1:47:54.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,...round and round.\N{\rCHT}沒有盡頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.93,1:48:07.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I changed it.\N{\rCHT}我要改變這一切{\r}
